OL,3,CWhy Orban's defeat will come as a blow
OL,4,Cto Putin, Netanyahu, and Trump
OL,6,FNot since Soviet tanks rolled across
OL,7,Fthe border in 1956 can the fate of
OL,8,FHungary have been the object of so
OL,9,Fmuch world attention.
OL,11,FIt is only a small, landlocked country
OL,12,Fof around 10 million people, but the
OL,13,Fousting of Viktor Orban last night is
OL,14,Fhugely consequential.
OL,26,@kD@HrpuD@Vrp
