OL,3,CWhy Orban's defeat will come as a blow
OL,4,Cto Putin, Netanyahu, and Trump
OL,6,FTo put it in context, President Trump
OL,7,Fsent his vice president to campaign,
OL,8,Fand he offered economic help to
OL,9,FHungarians if they re-elected Orban.
OL,10,FBenjamin Netanyahu recorded his
OL,11,Fsupport on video. President Putin used
OL,12,Fhis well-oiled foreign influence
OL,13,Fmachine extensively on Orban's behalf.
OL,15,FBut why the interest? For Putin, this
OL,16,Fwas the future of his man in the EU:
OL,17,FThe man who blocked sanctions, who fed
OL,18,Fhis intelligence services details of
OL,19,FEU Council discussions, who vetoed a
OL,20,Fhuge European loan to Ukraine.
OL,26,@kD@HrpuD@[rp
