OL,3,CWhy Orban's defeat will come as a blow
OL,4,Cto Putin, Netanyahu, and Trump
OL,6,FFor Netanyahu, Orban backed Israel
OL,7,Feven to the extent of blocking EU
OL,8,Fsanctions against violent West Bank
OL,9,Fsettlers. And for Trump, Orban was the
OL,10,Fkey to his ambitions to expand the
OL,11,FMAGA movement into Europe.
OL,13,FAs such, his ousting is a huge blow to
OL,14,Fall three, Putin most of all. Without
OL,15,FOrban, Ukraine will get its loan, and
OL,16,Fsanctions against Russia will be
OL,17,Frenewed.
OL,26,@kD@HrpnD@SrpqD@]rpwD@Drp
