OL,3,CWhy Orban's defeat will come as a blow
OL,4,Cto Putin, Netanyahu, and Trump
OL,6,FBut for Trump too, his 'anti-Midas
OL,7,Ftouch' in foreign elections scored
OL,8,Fanother remarkable result: first Mark
OL,9,FCarney in Canada, then Anthony
OL,10,FAlbanese in Australia, now Peter
OL,11,FMagyar have all won huge victories in
OL,12,Fthe face of Trump's opposition. Nigel
OL,13,FFarage and Jordan Bardella in France
OL,14,Fmay want to be wary of the 'Trump
OL,15,Feffect' after this.
OL,26,@kD@Hrp
