OL,3,CWhy Orban's defeat will come as a blow
OL,4,Cto Putin, Netanyahu, and Trump
OL,6,FThe size of Magyar's victory is
OL,7,Fsignificant as well. He has won a
OL,8,Fcomfortable two-thirds majority in
OL,9,Fparliament (138 seats out of 199),
OL,10,Fwith which he can undo the
OL,11,Fconstitutional changes brought about
OL,12,Fby Orban on his march towards an
OL,13,F'illiberal democracy'.
OL,15,FThe Orban loyalists, who will still
OL,16,Fcontrol many powerful positions in
OL,17,FHungary, will struggle to prevent a
OL,18,Fleader with such a massive mandate
OL,19,Ffrom undoing the Orban project.
OL,26,@kD@HrptD@GrpwD@Hrp{D@Urp
