OL,3,CWhy Orban's defeat will come as a blow
OL,4,Cto Putin, Netanyahu, and Trump
OL,6,FMany supporters of traditional liberal
OL,7,Fdemocracy had begun to wonder if there
OL,8,Fwas a democratic way back from strong-
OL,9,Fman rule once it had become
OL,10,Festablished. Hungary has proved,
OL,11,Fdecisively, that there is. Americans,
OL,12,Fin particular, will be taking notice.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
